title: Large 1-Bedroom w/ Oversized Windows for August Move!
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 47', 'OR Text', '47', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 893 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Lease with 47Hundred and come to know a rich Temescal lifestyle.', 'Offering beautifully designed apartment homes in a culturally rich neighborhood, our community blends gracefully into the surrounding environment to which we warmly belong.', 'As a resident, you will enjoy spacious interiors, fine amenities, pleasant architecture, and desirable proximity to myriad hallmarks of Oakland’s long history, along with local marketplaces, niche restaurants, and delightful boutique shops.', 'Features:', 'Spacious Walk-in Closets, Open-Concept Living Areas, Complete Stainless-Steel Appliance Packages, Great Natural Light with Large Floor to Ceiling Windows, Modern Custom-Wood Cabinetry, Distinctive Wood-Style Flooring, Cable and Fiber Optic Internet Available, Quartz Countertops Throughout, Lighted Bathroom Vanities & Tiled Showers, Designer Finishes & Tiled Kitchen Backsplashes, Full-Size Washer & Dryer, Patios Available*, Bar Seating Available*, Studio, One- and Two-Bedroom Residences', '*in Select Units', 'Community Amenities:', 'Surrounded by Restaurants, Entertainment & Shopping, Pet Friendly, UC Berkeley Minutes Away, Big House Beans Coffee, Underground Parking, Online Payments and Service Requests, Roof Top Terrace with Gas Grill and City Views, HealthySpot Partnership, ½ Block from Ford Go Bike Station, Bike Storage Room, Professional On-Site Management, Elevator Access', 'Pet Policy', 'We Love Pets--dog and cat friendly!', 'Contact for details.', 'Income Requirements:', '3 times monthly rent', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'Qc1ryhXSF4']
